      "other_details": {
        "en": {
          "provenance": "translation_service",
          "value": "Due to the prevailing anarchy in the country, I, Khagesh Ranjit, believe that if I get an opportunity to serve the nation and its people by providing a solution, it would be great. I have chosen the Aam Janata Party, which is a party favored by the nation, as it has thought about and implemented welfare, happiness, and prosperity for the country and its people. I have come this far by experiencing and choosing the Aam Janata Party as a worthy party for the common people."
        },
        "ne": {
          "provenance": "imported",
          "value": "देशमा अराजकताले पिरोलेकोले म खगेज रञ्जितले राष्ट्रलाई निकास दिइ जनता सेवा गर्ने मौका पाए हुन्थ्यो भनी राष्ट्रको मन पर्ने पार्टी जसले देश र जनताको बारे शुभ, शुख अनी संमृद्धीका लागि सोचेको र व्यवहारमा उतारेको पाइएकोले आम जनतालाई योग्य पार्टी आम जनता पार्टी नै रोजेर अनुभव गरेर यहाँ सम्म आएँ।"
        }
      },
      "qualification": {
